{Date="2017-07-14";Text=[=[In a Two-Headed Giant game, The Scarab God’s first ability causes the opposing team to lose life equal to twice the number of Zombies you control, although you scry only equal to the number of Zombies you control.]=];};
{Date="2017-07-14";Text=[=[If this creature dies but leaves your graveyard before the next end step, it will remain in its new zone.]=];};
