{Date="2018-03-16";Text=[=[If you cast a card “without paying its mana cost,” you can’t choose to cast it for any alternative costs, such as paying {3} to cast a morph card face down. You can, however, pay additional costs. If the card has any mandatory additional costs, such as that of Cathartic Reunion, those must be paid to cast the card.]=];};
